Heir Cash Advance
As An Heir, You Can Get Your Money Now
Heirs and beneficiaries frequently get stressed out both emotionally and financially during the probate process. Being stressed during this process is completely understandable since probate can be complicated, time consuming, and very costly. The cost of attorney’s fees, travel costs, estate taxes, and more adds up quickly. However, you can eliminate your financial stress by simply applying for an inheritance cash advance. In addition to paying the various costs associated with the probate process, you can also pay off pre-existing accrued bills, enable yourself to travel to the decedent’s funeral, and allow yourself time to visit with family and other loved ones during this difficult occasion without worrying about your finances. 
With Inheritance Funding Company, you can easily and quickly apply for a cash advance and eliminate your financial worries. Applying for a cash advance is free! And you can get your money in as little as 72 hours. Simply apply for your heir cash advance by filling out our brief and secure form below. You can also call one of our helpful customer service representatives at 1-800-944-2072. Save yourself from draining your savings, racking up immense credit card bills, or even going bankrupt during the costly probate process. Eliminate your financial stress today by contacting Inheritance Funding Company today!
Inheritance Funding Company provides inheritance cash advances to heirs of probate estates regardless of their credit status, employment or income history. As America’s oldest and largest provider of inheritance cash advances, we guarantee the lowest prices in the industry and are committed to delivering the best customer service. Your dedicated funding officer will keep in touch every step of the way and be available by phone or email throughout the process.
 
